OL,5, Richard Sharp says the BBC board will  
OL,6, review any potential conflicts of      
OL,7, interest he may have amid scrutiny over
OL,8, his links with Boris Johnson.          
OL,10,FClaims have emerged that the BBC       
OL,11,Fchairman was involved in securing a    
OL,12,Floan of up to #800,000 for the then-PM.
OL,14,FMr Sharp said he had not been involved 
OL,15,Fin a loan, a guarantee or arranging any
OL,16,Ffinancing.                             
OL,18,FIn a statement, he called the row "a   
OL,19,Fdistraction for the organisation, which
OL,20,FI regret".                             
